controls.label: Heading
controls.value: Thank you for choosing Support Warehouse to deliver your HPE Services Contract

controls.name: richtext-1
controls.label: Rich Text
controls.value:
Your account manager will now help you to manage your services contract going forward, and will arrange quarterly support reviews for you.

Now that you're set up with your services contract, remember to let your account manager know when you purchase new hardware, so we can add it to the contract. This will help to minimize your support administration going forward.

Your account manager can also help if you need any assistance accessing the HPE Support Center or getting started with the proprietary tools.

When it comes to renewal, we'll notify you 45 to 90 days in advance to make sure you've got enough time to renew the current support.

You'll also receive our Support Services Update, intended to highlight any changes or updates regarding IT in general, Hewlett Packard Enterprise and Support Warehouse.

controls.name: richtext-1
controls.label: Rich Text
controls.value:
To access the proactive deliverables included in your Proactive Care services contract, you'll need to access Proactive Care Central. To get started, visit:

http://www8.hp.com/be/en/business-services/proactive-support/proactive-care-central.html


If you require support from HPE, please call 0900-1170000.

Alternatively, you can log a support call through your HPE Support Center account.

For all of the contact options, visit: http://www8.hp.com/us/en/hpe/contact/support.html
